      "updated": 1784367277755,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "I Filtered by hash token\nI removed bcrypt for every session\ncheck because that's overkill;\nSHA-256 is fine for random\nsession tokens, and the DB lookup\nis the important part.\nalso fixed the typos.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "M_Cx4vqUAQC6ZqI-0b-sS",
      "originalText": "I Filtered by hash token\nI removed bcrypt for every session check because that's overkill; SHA-256 is fine for random session tokens, and the DB lookup is the important part.\nalso fixed the typos.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
