      "text": "Fixed it.\nIn HTTP request it would be fine\nbut in websocket NO.\nSo I changed user.id to\nparticipant.id",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "HE65zu6xsY0wcnqbRT2wq",
      "originalText": "Fixed it.\nIn HTTP request it would be fine but in websocket NO.\nSo I changed user.id to participant.id",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
